Class 'vplist': list of vertical profiles

Source: R/bioRad.R

Class for list of vertical profiles

# S3 method for vplist
summary(object, ...)

is.vplist(x)

Arguments

object

object of class 'vplist'
...

additional arguments affecting the summary produced.
x

object of class 'vplist'

Value

for is.vplist: TRUE if its argument is of class "vplist"

Details

An object of class vplist is a list containing only vp objects. By contrast, vpts objects contain time-ordered profiles of a single radar station. vplist objects can contain profiles of multiple radars.
